# Task Doc Rules

## Status Values

Only: `todo` | `in_progress` | `blocked` | `done` | `deferred`

## Task ID Format

`P{phase}-{seq}` e.g. P1-02, P6-18

## When Completing a Task

1. Set status `done` in [BACKLOG.md](../../docs/tasks/BACKLOG.md)
2. Check boxes in matching [phases/phase-*.md](../../docs/tasks/phases/)
3. Update [STATUS.md](../../docs/STATUS.md) progress counts
4. If API/schema changed → [api/schemas.md](../../docs/api/schemas.md)

## Picking Work

- Lowest incomplete V1 phase first (0 → 1 → 2 → 3 → 4 → 6)
- Skip `blocked` and `deferred` tasks
- Do not start Phase 5 without explicit user request

## V1 Complete

P6-18 Launch Review `done` + all [launch-criteria.md](../../docs/product/launch-criteria.md) checked.
